        </div>
Excellent condition, two bedrooms and one and a half bath two-story townhouse, 1,150 sq ft, located in a gated community, 1/8 mile from freeways 60, 215 and 91 and minutes to University of California, Riverside campus (UCR), Downtown Riverside, Riverside Community College, and Cal Baptist University.   This townhouse faces a greenbelt and has great view of the community swimming pool.  The unit has a carport with extra storage cabinet right behind the back patio for easy access, an extra parking space and a large outside patio right behind the property.  Plenty of street parkings.  Very open and spacious living room and dining room areas and half bath downstairs. Cozy master bedroom and second bedroom and full bath upstairs.  The home has tile flooring downstairs and bathrooms and Berber carpet upstairs.  The complex offers beautiful greenbelts, mature trees and swimming pool and is a gated community.<br>
<br>
Other features include ceiling fans throughout, centralized AC/heating system, refrigerator, gas range, dishwasher, in-unit washer/dryer, and much more.  An additional approx. 300 sq ft private enclosed patio perfect for BBQ and outdoor activities.  Location is convenient to local colleges, shopping, and freeway access. Just minutes to Riverside Golf Club, Riverside plaza and Riverside Galleries.  Trash is included in the rent. <br>
<br>
Available beginning of September.  Rental Application will be available online and sent through a private email link when requested.<br>
<br>
Application Fee: $42 per adult (18+) (non-refundable, charged by third-party service). <br>
$2,275 monthly rent amount with one-year lease. <br>
Security deposit equals 1 to 1½ month's rent.  <br>
<br>
